        <definition>typedef struct MR_InTreePathBuilder MR_InTreePathBuilder</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>MR_InTreePathBuilder</name>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>given a spanning tree of edges in the mesh (or forest in case of several connected components), prepares to build quickly a path along tree edges between any two vertices Generated from class <computeroutput>MR::InTreePathBuilder</computeroutput>. Supported <computeroutput>MR_PassBy</computeroutput> modes: <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_Copy</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_Move</computeroutput> (and <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_DefaultArgument</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_NoObject</computeroutput> if supported by the callee). </para>
        </detaileddescription>
